c: 2
v: 36
t: "fawqehma alshaytan fi alkhtyyt: ban wsws lahuma hataa 'aklana min alshjrt, ftsbb fi 'ikhrajhma min aljanat wneymha. waqal allah lhm: ahbituu 'iilaa alard, yeady baedukum bedana -ay adam whwa' walshytan- walakum fi al'ard aistiqrar w'iqamt, wantfae bma fiha 'iilaa waqt aintiha' ajalkm"